title: H3 After Dark #13
description:
On this episode of H3 After Dark the gang is all here and we're serving looks (mostly Hila) and goofs and gaffs! Together we discuss Rudy melting live on television, barbers with samurai swords, Gavin Newsom being a piece of shit, Vin-Book, and a whole lot more!
  The guy screaming STOP in the background of the Ace Family video
 Barber that cuts hair with Samurai Sword
 
Rudy Guiliani sweating through his hair dye   But that isn’t even the best part…
  
 Kenneth Copeland laughs at the media for declaring that Joe Biden has won the election and will become president.
 Pope likes tweet from IG girl
 Pictures of Harry Styles on cover of Vogue magazine
